{"tid":2086353,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"嘉士伯7月5日於全港20個地點派發逾10萬罐啤酒","createTime":"2020-06-30T08:55:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T09:27:58.000Z","uid":253829,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"da990298745c17c755fe3a0f4a83750fd3395cfc","tid":2086353,"uid":253829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T08:55:33.000Z","msg":"利物浦LIVERPOOL終於一嘗英超冠軍心願，由1992年已開始贊助利物浦的嘉士伯，將於7月5日於全港20個地點向市民派發逾10萬罐500毫升的嘉士伯啤酒。<br />\n<br />\n日期：7月5日 (星期日)<br />\n時間：12-5PM<br />\n派發地點如下：<br />\n<br />\n中環碼頭<br />\n炮台山地鐵站 A 出口<br />\n赤柱大街<br />\n灣仔駱克道/ 東角道<br />\n黃埔地鐵站 A 出口<br />\n觀塘地鐵站 A 出口<br />\n荔枝角地鐵站 A 出口<br />\n樂富地鐵站 A 出口<br />\n旺角豉油街<br />\n尖沙咀海防道<br />\n東涌美東街<br />\n葵芳地鐵站 D 出口<br />\n上水龍琛里<br />\n寳林地鐵站 B 出口<br />\n沙田地鐵站 B 出口<br />\n大圍地鐵站 B 出口<br />\n大埔地鐵站 A1 出口<br />\n荃灣楊屋道<br />\n屯門新墟 (近屯門市廣場二期)<br />\n元朗又新街"},{"pid":"35032d476adb0f82d28422b6a80deb755fa9ab37","tid":2086353,"uid":26773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T08:56:03.000Z","msg":"廢老排完又排<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dbfe76573e9ec15a967c386f350d4dc77e23a07","tid":2086353,"uid":124113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T08:56:46.000Z","msg":"排隊喎<br />\n大家唔係唔排下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82809c5923a80481ad7c466ba70665c342a7e255","tid":2086353,"uid":35930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T08:57:22.000Z","msg":"渣打夠贊助 又唔見派錢"},{"pid":"1a005db933b6bd945f282b2ec70995465cdce283","tid":2086353,"uid":3135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82809c5923a80481ad7c466ba70665c342a7e255","tid":2086353,"uid":35930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T08:57:22.000Z","msg":"渣打夠贊助 又唔見派錢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T09:25:21.000Z","msg":"渣打依啲垃圾唔好提啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dc24813532de1cd9dac97457a8eebb66ae45137","tid":20